* {{jalink|Jōgan|Q1075635|Jōgan}} 6 ({{jalink|864|Q25041}}) {{jalink|June 16|Q2653}}: Promoted from Junior Fifth Rank, Upper to Senior Fifth Rank, Lower (*Nihon Sandai Jitsuroku*) – recorded as “Sogatsuhiko-no-Kami.”

